{"tid":1801643,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"重要，滲透問題","createTime":"2019-12-28T19:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T19:26:31.000Z","uid":335379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d71cd9376b75e3521ae20eb1db22641b0d8c06","tid":1801643,"uid":335379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/271044893806518/permalink/302793623964978/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F271044893806518%2Fpermalink%2F302793623964978%2F&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=e8a8c1fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/271044893806518/permalink/302793623964978/</a><br />\n<br />\n上述講緊mon post黑心狗嘅問題<br />\n原諒我fc唔到<br />\n但必須正視<br />\n往後突擊活動請不要單獨行動及草率行事<br />\n是的，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">號召力可能會減弱</span><br />\n但咁樣<span style=\"font-size: large;\">可避免落單/人小而被咬</span><br />\n尤其是即日突擊<br />\n很難快速召集手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議</span><br />\n非重要或緊急<br />\n只響應日程表/提早一至兩天 召集之活動<br />\n同時，認清行動目標<br />\n如和你shop ，狗到落閘便要走<br />\n不應留戀戰場，亦不要落單<br />\n可考慮變裝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尤其年輕一輩</span><br />\n他們已成狗咬主要目標<br />\n在狗屋他們不懂保護自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可能有人會話</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁樣點對得住被咬/逝去手足</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">相信我，只有保護好自己</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">先至係對手足最好的聖誕禮物</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721，唔見人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請分享並宣介各人的看法<strong></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">發揮香港人嘅創造力</span></span>"},{"pid":"a103f5374c692d2281dc58e36491e27630dc8bee","tid":1801643,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:26:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}